		<img src="/css/img/add_comment.png" alt="Add Comment"> <a href="/posts/dessert-4-keep-your-cake-fresh-use-svn-head:480f4dd5-6fdc-4fd5-b64d-4df8cbdd56cb#CommentAddForm">Add Comment</a>	</div>
